<br>
I am just not sure if it is possible for a post-52 heal group to be stationed a good distance from the dragon lairs (e.g. the King room or beyond in Permafrost) such that the melees can run to them for healing? The main tank, however, do not have such a luxury due to summon and will need to have healers in the assault group to heal him. Has anyone tried such a tactic?<br>
<br>
